sqsRegionRefQualifier.prototype = {
	initialize: function() {
	},
	getRegionIDs: function(sys_id){
		var IDs = [];
		var relation = new GlideRecord("cmdb_rel_ci");
		relation.addQuery('child',sys_id);
		relation.query();
		
		while(relation.next()){
			var logicalDatacenter = new GlideRecord("cmdb_ci_logical_datacenter");
			logicalDatacenter.addQuery('sys_id',relation.getValue('parent'));
			logicalDatacenter.query();
			if(logicalDatacenter.next()){
				IDs.push(logicalDatacenter.sys_id+'');
			}
		}
		return IDs.toString();
	},
	type: 'sqsRegionRefQualifier'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>eric.williams@snc</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-05-02 19:51:45</sys_created_on><sys_id>4132ab4adbb9df0072465f135e96194a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>sqsRegionRefQualifier</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_4132ab4adbb9df0072465f135e96194a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>eric.williams@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-05-02 19:52:34</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="ecc_agent_script_include"><ecc_agent_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description/><name>AWSSQSJSProbe</name><script><![CDATA[var AWSSQSJSProbe = Class.create();
AWSSQSJSProbe.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AWSCloudAPIBase, {
	
	service: 'sqs',
	apiVersion: '2012-11-05',
	
	initialize: function() {
		this.location = probe.getParameter('location');
		this.endpointURL = probe.getParameter('endpointURL');
		this.deleteMessages = probe.getParameter('deleteMessages');
		this.maxMessages = probe.getParameter('numberOfMessages');
		this.maxRequests = probe.getParameter('maxRequests');
		
		var credential_id = probe.getParameter('credential_id');
		
		var credentialProvider = new  Packages.com.snc.commons.credentials.CredentialsProviderFactory.getCredentialsProvider();
		var credential = credentialProvider.getCredentialByID(credential_id);
		this.identity = credential.getAttributeByName('access_key');
		this.credentials = credential.getAttributeByName('secret_key');
	
		var parameters = new Packages.java.util.HashMap();
		var headers = new Packages.java.util.HashMap();
		
		parameters.put('Location',this.location);
		parameters.put('Credentials',this.credentials);
		parameters.put('Identity',this.identity);
		parameters.put('EndpointURL',this.endpointURL);
		
		AWSCloudAPIBase.prototype.initialize.call(this, parameters, headers);
	},
	
	receiveMessages: function(){
		var action = "ReceiveMessage";
		var actionParameters = {};
			var messages = [];
			var messageIDs;
			
			var deleteOnReceipt = this.deleteMessages;
			
			for (var requestCount=0;requestCount < this.maxRequests;requestCount++){
				messageIDs = [];
				actionParameters.MaxNumberOfMessages = this.maxMessages;
				
				var response = this.executeAction(action, actionParameters);
				
				if(response.ReceiveMessageResult === null) {
					break;
				}
				else {
					if(Array.isArray(response.ReceiveMessageResult.Message)){
						for (var index=0;index < response.ReceiveMessageResult.Message.length;index++){
							messageIDs.push({
								'id':response.ReceiveMessageResult.Message[index].MessageId,
								'receiptHandle':response.ReceiveMessageResult.Message[index].ReceiptHandle
							});
							messages.push(response.ReceiveMessageResult.Message[index].Body);
						}
					}
					else{
						messageIDs.push({
							'id':response.ReceiveMessageResult.Message.MessageId,
							'receiptHandle':response.ReceiveMessageResult.Message.ReceiptHandle
						});
						messages.push(response.ReceiveMessageResult.Message.Body);
					}
				}
				
				if(deleteOnReceipt){
					var deleteResponse = this.deleteMessageBatch(messageIDs);
				}
			}
			return JSON.stringify(messages);
		},
		
		deleteMessageBatch: function(messageBatch){
			var action = "DeleteMessageBatch";
			var actionParameters = {};
				
				for(var index=0;index<messageBatch.length;index++){
					actionParameters["DeleteMessageBatchRequestEntry."+(index+1)+'.Id'] = messageBatch[index].id;
					actionParameters["DeleteMessageBatchRequestEntry."+(index+1)+'.ReceiptHandle'] = messageBatch[index].receiptHandle;
				}
				
				var response = this.executeAction(action,actionParameters);
				return response;
			},
			
			type: 'AWSSQSJSProbe'
		});]]></script><sys_class_name>ecc_agent_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-04-20 13:03:44</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>c2e154d6db29570072465f135e9619d0</sys_id><sys_mod_count>64</sys_mod_count><sys_name>AWSSQSJSProbe</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>ecc_agent_script_include_c2e154d6db29570072465f135e9619d0</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>eric.williams@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-05-02 19:46:35</sys_updated_on></ecc_agent_script_include></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.AWSSQSProbeRunner</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>AWSSQSProbeRunner</name><script><![CDATA[var AWSSQSProbeRunner = Class.create();
AWSSQSProbeRunner.prototype = {
	initialize: function() {
	},
	
	runScheduledJob: function(awsConfigDefinitionID){
		var awsConfigDefinitionGR = new GlideRecord('u_aws_config_sqs_integration');
		if (!awsConfigDefinitionGR.get(awsConfigDefinitionID)){
			gs.error("AWS SQS Probe Runner: No config definition found for id {0}",awsConfigDefinitionID);
			return;
		}
		
		if(awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_active == false){
			gs.error("AWS SQS Probe Runner: Config Definition {0} not active",awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_name);
			this.setJobActiveFlag(awsConfigDefinitionGR);
			return;
		}
		this.runProbe(awsConfigDefinitionGR);
	},
	
	createJob: function(awsConfigDefinitionGR){
		var jobGR = new GlideRecord('sysauto_script');
		jobGR.initialize();
		jobGR.name = "AWS SQS Config Probe Scheduled Job: " + awsConfigDefinitionGR.getDisplayValue();
		jobGR.active = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_active;
		jobGR.run_type = 'periodically';
		jobGR.run_period.setDateNumericValue(awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_poll_frequency * 60000);
		jobGR.run_start.setDisplayValue(gs.nowDateTime());
		jobGR.script = 'var probeRunner = new AWSSQSProbeRunner();\n'
						+ 'probeRunner.runScheduledJob("' + awsConfigDefinitionGR.sys_id + '");';
		jobGR.insert();
		
		return jobGR;
	},
	
	deleteJob: function(awsConfigDefinitionGR){
		if(gs.nil(awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_scheduled_job)){
			gs.error("AWS SQS Probe Runner: Job not found for deletion on {0}",awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_name);
			return;
		}
		var jobGR = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_scheduled_job.getRefRecord();
		jobGR.deleteRecord();
	},
	
	setJobActiveFlag: function(awsConfigDefinitionGR){
		if(gs.nil(awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_scheduled_job)){
			gs.error("AWS SQS Probe Runner: Job not found for activation/deactivation on {0}",awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_name);
			return;
		}
		var jobGR = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_scheduled_job.getRefRecord();
		jobGR.active = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_active;
		jobGR.update();
	},
	
	updateJobInterval: function(awsConfigDefinitionGR){
		if(gs.nil(awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_scheduled_job)){
			gs.error("AWS SQS Probe Runner: Job not found for interval update on {0}",awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_name);
			return;
		}
		var jobGR = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_scheduled_job.getRefRecord();
		jobGR.run_period.setDateNumericValue(awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_poll_frequency * 60000);
		jobGR.update();
	},
	
	updateJobName: function(awsConfigDefinitionGR){
		if(gs.nil(awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_scheduled_job)){
			gs.error("AWS SQS Probe Runner: Job not found for name update on {0}",awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_name);
			return;
		}
		var jobGR = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_scheduled_job.getRefRecord();
		jobGR.name = "AWS SQS Config Probe Scheduled Job: " + awsConfigDefinitionGR.getDisplayValue();
		jobGR.update();
	},
	
	runProbe: function(awsConfigDefinitionGR){
		var region = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_region.region.getValue();
		var accountNumber = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_credentials.account_id.getValue();
		var queueName = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_sqs_queue_name.getValue();
		var deleteMessagesFlag = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_delete_messages_after_receipt.toString();
		var numberOfMessages = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_max_messages_per_request.getValue();
		var numberOfRequests = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_max_requests_per_poll.getValue();
		var credentialId = awsConfigDefinitionGR.u_credentials.discovery_credentials.getValue();
		
		var endpointURL = "https://sqs." + region + ".amazonaws.com/" + accountNumber + "/" + queueName;
		
		var probe = SncProbe.get('AWS-SQS-Config-JS');
		probe.addParameter("credential_id",credentialId);
		probe.addParameter("location",region);
		probe.addParameter("deleteMessages",deleteMessagesFlag);
		probe.addParameter("numberOfMessages",numberOfMessages);
		probe.addParameter("maxRequests",numberOfRequests);
		probe.addParameter("endpointURL",endpointURL);
		
		var msf = new MIDServerFinder();
		msf.setCapabilities(["AWS"]);
		
		return probe.create(msf.getMIDServers()[0]);
	},
	
	type: 'AWSSQSProbeRunner'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-04-30 20:41:32</sys_created_on><sys_id>321a9d29dbb19f0072465f135e9619b6</sys_id><sys_mod_count>16</sys_mod_count><sys_name>AWSSQSProbeRunner</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_321a9d29dbb19f0072465f135e9619b6</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>eric.williams@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-05-01 19:07:38</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
